{
  "text": "I am wrong. This instrument is not aware of the appropriate apparel for this work, as inocorings occur in the regions of the what you may call a seventh chakra, as you speak of these energy centers filtering through the sixth and so forth. The entities, other or base chakras, become somewhat de-enerized. Thus, this entity should be more careful in its selection of a worn apparel for the part of the body complex you call the feet. May we answer any other brief questions?",
